Macros

macro bindProcs(w: webwsi; scope: string; n: untyped): untyped
bind procs like:
proc fn[T, U](arg: T): U
proc fn[T](arg: T)
proc fn()

to webwsi w, in scope scope then you can invode in js side, like this:

scope.fn(arg)
